{"id": "art-25125", "label": "Art. 25125", "title": "Art. 25125", "slug": "art-25125", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1643292601\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1680\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1643292601\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>25</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1909184620\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1679\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1909184620\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii sau, dup&#259; caz, membrii\ndirectoratului fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune întocmesc un raport, cu dou&#259; <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iuni</span>,\nuna destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cealalt&#259; destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>,\nsau dou&#259; rapoarte distincte în care explic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\njustific&#259; aspectele juridice <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> economice\nale fuziunii transfrontaliere, explicând <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> pentru <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>.\nRaportul precizeaz&#259;, în special, <span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span>\nfuziunii transfrontaliere asupra <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\neconomice viitoare a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2011472196\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1678\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2011472196\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259;/În raportul\ndestinat <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> sunt precizate cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_772142356\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1677\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_772142356\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere pentru <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_470945131\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1676\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_470945131\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social pentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nîn care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nexercit&#259; dreptul de retragere din societate, inclusiv metoda/metodele\nfolosit&#259;(e) pentru calcularea acestuia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1576976832\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1675\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1576976832\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)rata de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nmetoda/metodele de calcul folosit&#259;(e) pentru calcularea acesteia, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cuantumul eventualelor <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span>\nîn numerar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_673213320\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1674\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_673213320\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)drepturile de care beneficiaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>30</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1951278948\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1673\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1951278948\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport\ndestinat&#259;/Raportul destinat <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> nu\neste obligatorie/obligatoriu în cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; cu asociat unic <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nîn cazul în care <span class=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nau convenit s&#259; <span class=SpellE>renun&#355;e</span> la aceast&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>cerin&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_348093338\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1672\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_348093338\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport destinat&#259;/În raportul\ndestinat <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sunt precizate cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_651189572\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1671\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_651189572\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span> fuziunii\ntransfrontaliere asupra raporturilor de munc&#259;, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, m&#259;surile necesare pentru <span class=SpellE>men&#355;inerea</span>\nacestor raporturi de munc&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_307965029\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1670\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_307965029\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)orice modificare <span class=SpellE>substan&#355;ial&#259;</span>\na <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> de angajare/de munc&#259;\naplicabile sau cu privire la sediile <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nparticipante la fuziune;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_903698089\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1669\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_903698089\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)modul în care elementele prev&#259;zute la lit. a) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> b) afecteaz&#259; filialele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nparticipante la fuziune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_443722345\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1668\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_443722345\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Sec&#355;iunea</span> din raport\ndestinat&#259;/Raportul destinat <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> nu\neste obligatorie/obligatoriu în cazul în care activitatea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nparticipante la fuziune <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este\ncazul, a filialelor acestora este derulat&#259; exclusiv de c&#259;tre\nadministratori sau, dup&#259; caz, de membrii consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> ori, dup&#259; caz, de membrii\nconsiliului de supraveghere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ai\ndirectoratului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_331580241\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1667\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_331580241\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data întrunirii\nadun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259; aprobe fuziunea transfrontalier&#259;,\nraportul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) sau, dup&#259; caz, <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span>\ncorespunz&#259;toare a raportului sau rapoartele distincte se pune/se pun la <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau, în cazul în care nu au fost <span\nclass=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;i</span>\nai <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span>,\npentru fiecare societate participant&#259; la fuziune, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nîn format electronic, prin <span class=SpellE>afi&#351;are</span> pe pagina de\ninternet a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>28</sup> alin. (3), sau\nprin transmitere pe cale electronic&#259;. În cazul în care nu este\nnecesar&#259; aprobarea fuziunii de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259;, raportul\nsau rapoartele se pune/se pun la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data\nîntrunirii adun&#259;rii generale a oric&#259;reia dintre celelalte <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> care fuzioneaz&#259;. În cazul în care <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i> aplicabil&#259; fiec&#259;reia\ndintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la fuziune\nprevede exceptarea de la aprobarea fuziunii de c&#259;tre adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, raportul sau\nrapoartele se pune/se pun la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data\nstabilit&#259; pentru aprobarea acesteia de c&#259;tre consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sau, dup&#259; caz, de directorat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_776233285\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1666\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_776233285\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<span class=SpellE>Reprezentan&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau, dac&#259; nu au fost <span\nclass=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;i</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span> au dreptul s&#259; formuleze o opinie\ncu privire la raportul destinat/la <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> din\nraport destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>, cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 5 zile înainte de data întrunirii adun&#259;rii\ngenerale convocate s&#259; aprobe proiectul de fuziune transfrontalier&#259;.\nOpinia se anexeaz&#259; raportului, iar administratorii/membrii directoratului\ntransmit r&#259;spuns motivat <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de\nopinia formulat&#259;, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> cu o zi\nînaintea acestei date. <span class=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span> sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;i</span> cu privire la opinia formulat&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nsau, dup&#259; caz, de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1485635474\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1665\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1485635474\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)În cazul în care, în conformitate cu alin. (3), se <span\nclass=SpellE>renun&#355;&#259;</span> la <span class=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span>\ndin raport destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, iar <span\nclass=SpellE>sec&#355;iunea</span> destinat&#259; <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nnu este obligatorie, fiind aplicabile prevederile alin. (5), raportul nu este\nnecesar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_428037168\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1664\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_428037168\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Alin. (1)-(8) nu aduc atingere drepturilor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> procedurilor de informare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nconsultare aplicabile <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>,\nprev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>467/2006</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nstabilirea cadrului general de informare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nconsultare a <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2005</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nconstituirea, organizarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ionarea</span>\ncomitetului european de întreprindere, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nalin. (7) aplicându-se în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1702166216\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1663\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1702166216\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Administratorii sau, dup&#259; caz, membrii\ndirectoratului fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune informeaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nînainte de data întrunirii adun&#259;rii generale convocate pentru aprobarea\nfuziunii transfrontaliere sau, cel mai târziu, în cadrul acesteia, dac&#259;,\nulterior datei întocmirii proiectului comun de fuziune transfrontalier&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a raportului/rapoartelor\nprev&#259;zut/prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), au intervenit modific&#259;ri\nsemnificative privind activele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau nivelul veniturilor acesteia, în special în cazul în care acestea ar\ndetermina o rat&#259; de schimb diferit&#259;, o alocare diferit&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social la <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare sau un <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;</span> diferit al <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social pentru <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\ncare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>-ar exercita dreptul de retragere.</span></p>"}